QUICK REFERENCE – PROTOCOL B WORD COUNTS & MAPPINGS
- d4 / d8 / d10: 3 words per die (sum → last digit)
- d12: 2 words total (1 coin [0/6] + 1 bucket [1–6])
- d20: 4 words total (1 coin [0/10] + 3 base [sum → last digit])
- d100 / d%: 6 words total (3 tens + 3 units)
- Coin: Bucket 1–3 = 0, Bucket 4–6 = 6 (d12) or 10 (d20)
- d%: Read d100 as percentile (00–99 or 00=100 per system rules)


